situation: A prestressed concrete beam is 400mm wide and 800mm deep. The prestressing tendons are located 200mm below the neutral axis of the beam. The total prestressing force (less losses) is 1200kN.

subquestions.question: Determine the stress in the bottom of the beam due to the prestressing force, in MPa.
Determine the stress in the top of the beam due to the prestressing force, in MPa.
What external moment (in kN-m) can act on the beam to just make the stress in the beam at the bottom zero?
